{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winnu Waigo Gih- \nmis pa labbas Rohkas to tſchet-\nru/ bija weena Zilweka Waigs/ \nnn weena Lauwa Waigs/ un pa\nkreifas Rohkas to tſchetru bija\nteem weena Wehrſcha Waigs/ \nir weena Ehrge Waigs bij teem\ntſchetreem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir winnu Waigi un win-\nnu Spahrni bija no augtche-\nnes faſchkelti/ ikweenam bija di-\nwi falikti/ un diviapklahe win-\nnu Meeſas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee gahje ikweens tee-\nscham preeſch tewig prohjam/\nkurp tas Wehjch dsinnahs/ turp\ntee gahje/ un ne apgreesaſs/ kad\ntee gahje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Lihdsiba to Sweh-\nru bija redsama/ itt ka Ohgles/\nkas ar Ugguni deg/ ka to Lahpu\nGihmis/ tas pats Ugguns tur-\nrejahs starp teem Swehreem.\nUn tam Uggunim bija Spoh-\nschums/ un no ta Ugguns isleh-\nze Sibbins.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Swehri tezzeja/\nun atgreesaſs itt ka kahda Sib-\nbina Gihmis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad es tohs Sweh-\nrus redseju/raugt/tad bija weens\nSkrittelts wirs Semmes fah-\nnis teem Swehreem/ itt ka tſchet-\ni Skritteſti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "To Skritteſti Gihmis\nin winnu Darbs bija ka weens\nTurköſa Akmins/ un tſcheem\nſchetrecin bija weena Lihdsiba/\nin winnu Gihmis un winnu\nDarbs bija itt ka buhtu weens\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad teem bij ja-eet/ tad\ngahje tee us faaweem tſchetreem\nStuhreem/ un kad tee gahje/ tad\ntee ne greesahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winnu Lohki bija pa-\nfant augſt/ un winnu Lohki bi-\nja pilli ar Azzim/ witsapkahrt\npee teem tſchetreem Skrittekeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad tee Swehri gah-\nje/ gahje tee Skritteki fahnis\nwinneem/ un kad tee Swehri\nno Semmes uszehlahs/ tad us-\ngehlahs arridsan tee Skrittekf.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kurp tas Wehjch dsin-\nnahs/ turp tee gahje/ un tee\nSkritteki fahnis teem uszehlahs/\njo weens dſhwos Gars bija eekſch\nteem Skrittekeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tee gahje/ tad ir ſchee\ngahje/ un kad tee ſtahweia/ ſtah-\nweja ir ſchee/ un kad tee no\nSemmes uszehlahs/ tad ir tee\nSkritteki fahnis teem uszehlahs/\njo weens dſhwos Gars bija eekſch\nteem Skrittekeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wirs to Swehru\nGalwahm bija tas ta patt/ ka\nweena Jſplattijums no breeſmi-\nga Leddus/ no augtchenes wirs\nwinnu Galwahm iſplattihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un appakſch ta Jſplatti-\njuma bija winnu Spahrni tee-\nscham weens pee ohtra / ikwee-\nnam bij diwt/ kas winnu apſe-\ndse weena Puſſe/ un atkat dt-\nw/ kas winnu Mcefas apſede\nohtra Puſſe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad tee gahje/ dsirdeju\nes winnu Spahrno Ribvescha-\nnu/\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
